413
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mi govorimo o njeme tek nakon drugog

414
00:24:29,599 --> 00:24:33,200
[SPEAKER_00] Vatikanskog koncila kao službenom pokretu u crkvi.

415
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:36,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo su bile neke druge reforme,

416
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo recu tako,

417
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] koje su također, mislim,

418
00:24:38,839 --> 00:24:42,140
[SPEAKER_00] nositelji su bili karizmatični ljudi,

419
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] pa nekad i sa dobrim idejama,

420
00:24:43,779 --> 00:24:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] koje su poslije krenule u krivo,

421
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali, kažem, nikad nisu ideje ili karizme

422
00:24:48,559 --> 00:24:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] bila uzrok raskola,

423
00:24:49,819 --> 00:24:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego je uvijek bila određena vrsta

424
00:24:53,039 --> 00:24:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] neposlušnosti pojedinca.

425
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, ovo, gdje mi sad,

426
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi raščlanio možda ovu problematiku?

427
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ostat uvijek vjeran crkvi,

428
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] ostati stvarno u duhu poniznosti

429
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] i traži neka gospodin

430
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:08,400
