453
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] kako je moli itd.

454
00:26:12,079 --> 00:26:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ona zapravo štiti toga pojedinca

455
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] od izrabljivanja.

456
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne želi da se neka osoba

457
00:26:19,599 --> 00:26:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima određenu vrstu karizme unuta crkve

458
00:26:23,019 --> 00:26:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] pretvori u babu gataru

459
00:26:25,799 --> 00:26:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] koja je na TV programu

460
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:31,299
