461
00:26:31,299 --> 00:26:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne želi podavnicima

462
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] izrabljivanje te osobe

463
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:38,079
