464
00:26:38,079 --> 00:26:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] I onda i ovo možda

465
00:26:40,079 --> 00:26:41,759
[SPEAKER_00] što nam na početku izgleda

466
00:26:41,759 --> 00:26:43,660
[SPEAKER_00] kao određena vrsta

467
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] nerazumijevanja

468
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] ili određena vrsta oluja

469
00:26:46,819 --> 00:26:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] se zapravo poslije pokazuje

470
00:26:49,859 --> 00:26:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] u toj prizi

471
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] jerarhijske crkve

472
00:26:52,539 --> 00:26:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] i za osobu i za pokret

473
00:26:54,119 --> 00:26:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] kao određena vrsta možda je

474
00:26:55,980 --> 00:26:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] brušenja ili poliranja

475
00:26:57,980 --> 00:27:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] te stvarnosti dara, duha svetoga

476
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] i karizme

477
00:27:01,059 --> 00:27:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] unutar određene zajednice

478
00:27:02,859 --> 00:27:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] i ispadne poslije stvarno dobro.

479
00:27:04,980 --> 00:27:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] Zato kažem, ja ne volim

480
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] previše mirne situacije

481
