[SPEAKER_00] i meni je drago

482
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad postoji ovako i propitivanje

483
00:27:13,059 --> 00:27:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] i međusobno ubažavanje

484
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] zato što ono od nas traži veće napore

485
