[SPEAKER_00] veći napori

487
00:27:20,519 --> 00:27:22,200
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek onda Bog potpomogne

488
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,259
[SPEAKER_00] i većom milošću.

489
00:27:23,259 --> 00:27:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] I ovdje da bi završio

490
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:25,579
