499
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad pretrpi određenu vrstu gubitka

500
00:27:43,180 --> 00:27:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim da se ne bi smijeli

501
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,700
