[SPEAKER_00] druge božanske osobe.

515
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] tako da kažem

516
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] nekad kad smo previše uspjereni

517
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] tome samo

518
00:28:20,059 --> 00:28:22,420
